OL,3,CReform call as children suffer
OL,4,C'trauma' through NI court cases
OL,6,FCalls are growing for the reform of
OL,7,Fthe family court system including the
OL,8,Fintroduction of a way to better
OL,9,Fprotect children involved in cases
OL,10,Fwere domestic abuse may be a factor.
OL,12,FA number of women UTV has spoken to
OL,13,Fclaim they have been threatened with
OL,14,Fcourt sanctions and their children are
OL,15,Fexperiencing further trauma.
