OL,3,CReform call as children suffer
OL,4,C'trauma' through NI court cases
OL,6,FDame Siobhan Keegan - Northern
OL,7,FIreland's most senior judge - said
OL,8,Fthere is ongoing training on the issue
OL,9,Fand judges are aware of the sensitive
OL,10,Fnature of the cases. She highlighted
OL,11,Fthe complex nature of the cases but
OL,12,Fsaid proceedings could be more
OL,13,Ftransparent.
OL,15,FLast year UTV spoke exclusively to a
OL,16,Fnumber of women who alleged they were
OL,17,Fthreatened with penal notices,
OL,18,Fcontempt of court, and the potential
OL,19,Fremoval of their children.
