OL,3,CReform call as children suffer
OL,4,C'trauma' through NI court cases
OL,6,FTwelve months on, they say nothing has
OL,7,Fchanged with some claiming their
OL,8,Ftreatment has got worse.
OL,10,FCarol, not her real name, spoke to UTV
OL,11,Fdirectly after her latest family court
OL,12,Fappearance.
OL,14,FShe alleges her ex-partner and father
OL,15,Fof her four-year-old daughter
OL,16,Fassaulted her both when she was
OL,17,Fpregnant and when her child was a baby
OL,18,Fin her arms.
