OL,3,CReform call as children suffer
OL,4,C'trauma' through NI court cases
OL,6,FCarol says she reported the abuse to
OL,7,Fpolice but no further action was
OL,8,Ftaken. She claims abuse is continuing
OL,9,Fthrough the family courts.
OL,11,FShe claims she has been blamed for the
OL,12,Ftrauma her daughter is suffering.
OL,14,F"She has developed a stutter, and has
OL,15,Fbegun bedwetting. She wakes in the
OL,16,Fmiddle screaming and crying, thinking
OL,17,Fsomeone is going to take her off me
OL,18,Fand that has been completely turned
OL,19,Faround on me.
