OL,3,CReform call as children suffer
OL,4,C'trauma' through NI court cases
OL,6,F"Do whatever you want to me but when
OL,7,Fmy children are involved and you're
OL,8,Ftrying to protect your children, and
OL,9,Fit's held against you, it's used
OL,10,Fagainst you, It's one of the hardest
OL,11,Fthings," she added.
OL,13,FUTV has spoken to a range of women who
OL,14,Fshare similar experiences.
OL,16,FThey all allege they've been
OL,17,Fthreatened with penal notices,
OL,18,Fcontempt of court and the potential
OL,19,Fremoval of their children.
