OL,4,C'trauma' through NI court cases
OL,6,FHarriett Long from Women's Aid says
OL,7,F80% of the mothers and children they
OL,8,Fwork with are struggling with their
OL,9,Ftreatment in the family courts.
OL,11,F"We were recently subpoenaed to be in
OL,12,Ffamily court but were never called
OL,13,Fupon," she said.
