OL,3,CReform call as children suffer
OL,4,C'trauma' through NI court cases
OL,6,F"The child in question was terrified
OL,7,Fof this dad who had assaulted her
OL,8,Fsiblings who had done a lot of violent
OL,9,Fthings on the home which were very
OL,10,Fdestructive but the abuser had not
OL,11,Ftold his legal team about any of these
OL,12,Fincidents and had really played down
OL,13,Fthe child's fear."
OL,15,FThe organisation is now calling for
OL,16,Freform of the system.
OL,26,@uD@RO]
