OL,3,CReform call as children suffer
OL,4,C'trauma' through NI court cases
OL,6,F"It needs to be more trauma informed
OL,7,Fand I know that phrase can be a bit
OL,8,Foverused but taking into account the
OL,9,Fimpact of developmental trauma on a
OL,10,Fchild at that stage in their
OL,11,Fdevelopment is really important
OL,12,Fbecause there are really long term
OL,13,Fdamages that can be done," she said.
OL,15,FIn a recent interview with UTV
OL,16,FNorthern Ireland's top judge maintains
OL,17,Fthis area of law is complex but that
OL,18,Fshe is open to reform including
OL,19,Fjournalists being allowed in to report
OL,20,Fon proceedings.
