OL,3,CReform call as children suffer
OL,4,C'trauma' through NI court cases
OL,6,FDame Siobhan Keegan said she has been
OL,7,Fcontacted by both concerned mothers
OL,8,Fand fathers.
OL,10,FShe said: "There's no hierarchy in any
OL,11,Fof this. But I think we have to be
OL,12,Freceptive to the fact that any ongoing
OL,13,Frelationship can continue to
OL,14,Fperpetuate that type of controlling
OL,15,Fbehaviour.
OL,17,F"And family judges will see this. And
OL,18,Fas I've said through training and
OL,19,Fthrough public conversation, become
OL,20,Fmore aware of it.
OL,26,@rD@KOUyD@AOU
