OL,3,CReform call as children suffer
OL,4,C'trauma' through NI court cases
OL,6,F"So we do need to continue our
OL,7,Ftraining on it. We do need to be alive
OL,8,Fto the issue. And what I would say is
OL,9,Fit is a very complicated area. And
OL,10,Fthat's why I do think that the family
OL,11,Fcourt should be more open and more
OL,12,Ftransparent," she added.
OL,14,FLast year a group of women met with
OL,15,Fthe victims of crime commissioner
OL,16,Fwhose office is carrying out research
OL,17,Finto this area which is due to be
OL,18,Fpublished in the coming months.
