OL,3,CReform call as children suffer
OL,4,C'trauma' through NI court cases
OL,6,FIn a statement, Justice Minister Naomi
OL,7,FLong added: "The paramount
OL,8,Fconsideration should be for children's
OL,9,Fwelfare, especially when domestic
OL,10,Fabuse has been a factor.
OL,12,FShe said she was "working with the
OL,13,Fchief justice to consider the
OL,14,Fpotential for some media reporting,
OL,15,Fwhile still protecting the privacy of
OL,16,Fthe families involved and that there
OL,17,Fare benefits to increasing the
OL,18,Fopenness of family courts."
